full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 No .8402/196 REPORT July 28, 9 1933. WONG GUCK ON (Wong Kwo ck on), this applicant, is identified by San Pedro file, N .7402/99, showing his admission as the son of a U. S.Citizen on No vember 7, 1932, and issued certificate of identity, No.67098, herewith. His present statement is in good accord with that givemat time of applying for admission. He will be accompanied to China by his brother Wong Kwork Hai. A favorable recommendation is respectfully submitted. Jenardine to NARDINI, Immigrant Inspector.
